description: A Black Lives Matter rally is held as Guernsey relaxes nearly all of its lockdown restrictions.
title: Guernsey anti-racism demo marks end to social distancing
title_page: Guernsey anti-racism demo marks end to social distancing - BBC News
maintext: Augustus Mbanasor, who moved from London six months ago to work in finance, said: "It's always good to see your community being supported in a place that's fairly new to you."
